Significant challenges include:
Erosion of knowledge due to globalization, urbanization, and environmental change.
Ethical issues: Informed consent, benefit-sharing, avoiding extractivism.
Methodological: Standardization for broader syntheses; integrating quantitative and qualitative data.
Decolonial needs: Greater Indigenous authorship and control. 

